1. Check Docker Version
docker --version
2. Run Netdata Container
docker run -d --name=netdata -p 19999:19999 netdata/netdata
3.Check Running Containers
docker ps
4. Check All Containers (including stopped)
docker ps -a
5. Inspect Container Details
docker inspect netdata
# or by ID
docker inspect 3f86b7511c0c
6. View Container Logs
docker logs netdata
7. Stop a Container
docker stop netdata
8. Remove (Delete) a Container
docker rm netdata
9. List Docker Images
docker images
10. Remove an Image
docker rmi netdata/netdata

